column.name: SFLAG
column.Comment: 状态标志 0 未签收 1 已签收

column.name: URI
column.Comment: The uri is the part of the file url after the base dir has been removed. See MD_APPLICATION for base dir

column.name: TYPE
column.Comment: This will denote the type of file we have, including DIR, FILE (text), BINARY, IGNORE (where we choose to ignore files)

column.name: STATE
column.Comment: State will be how this file is operated on. For example. it will be OPEN, NEW, FIXED, IGNORED, REVIEWED, COMPLETE

column.name: LANGUAGE
column.Comment: Language of the file that has been processed.

column.name: DESCRIPTION
column.Comment: Overview of what the application does.

column.name: BASE_DIR
column.Comment: This is the base src directory for the application. It could be an svn checkout, a clearcase view or something similar

column.name: OUTPUT_DIR
column.Comment: This is the output directory where the scanner will present the converted files, if there are converted or modified.

column.name: BACKUP_DIR
column.Comment: This is the directory in which the application files are backed up if a backp is chosen

column.name: INPLACE
column.Comment: Designates whether the changes have been made inplace, in the source directory or not

column.name: PROJECT_ID_FK
column.Comment: project of the database(s) this application relates to

column.name: PATTERN
column.Comment: Pattern used to search source file for interesting artifiacts

column.name: STRING_FOUND
column.Comment: String found in source from the pattern supplied

column.name: STRING_REPLACED
column.Comment: This is the string which replace the string found if it was replaced.

column.name: TYPE
column.Comment: This is the type of the replacement. It could be a straight replace from a replacement pattern, or we could have passed the string to a translator which would change the string depending on the database.

column.name: STATUS
column.Comment: Pattern used to search source file for interesting artifiacts

column.name: DUE_DATE
column.Comment: Due date is used by the TODO mechanism to manage the validation and work to complete this change
